'''七氧化二氯'''是一种[[氯|氯]]的[[氧化物|氧化物]]，化学式为Cl<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub>，是[[高氯酸|高氯酸]]的[[酸酐|酸酐]]。可由高氯酸与[[五氧化二磷|五氧化二磷]]反应製得。<ref name=Holl>Holleman, A. F.; Wiberg, E. "Inorganic Chemistry" Academic Press: San Diego, 2001. ISBN 0-12-352651-5.</ref>
:2HClO<sub>4</sub>  +  P<sub>4</sub>O<sub>10</sub>  →  Cl<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub>  +  H<sub>2</sub>P<sub>4</sub>O<sub>11</sub>

它也可以由氯气和[[臭氧|臭氧]]反应而成。<ref>{{Cite journal| first1 = A. C.| title = The Formation of Chlorine Heptoxide on Illumination of Mixtures of Chlorine and Ozone| first2 = G. K.| last1 = Byrns| journal = Journal of the American Chemical Society| volume = 56| issue = 5| pages = 1250–1251| year = 1934| doi = 10.1021/ja01320a506| last2 = Rollefson}}</ref>七氧化二氯会慢慢[[水解|水解]]成[[高氯酸|高氯酸]], 不在水溶液里的高氯酸也是很危险的。

七氧化二氯受热易分解：
:2Cl<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub>  →  2Cl<sub>2</sub>  +  7O<sub>2</sub>  (ΔH = 135 kJ/mol)

==结构==

Cl<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub> 是一个吸热的分子，意味着它本质上是不稳定的，会随着能量的释放而分解为其组成元素:<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Martin|first=Jan M. L|date=2006-10-12|title=Heats of formation of perchloric acid, HClO<sub>4</sub>, and perchloric anhydride, Cl<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub>. Probing the limits of W1 and W2 theory|journal=Journal of Molecular Structure: THEOCHEM|series=Modelling Structure and Reactivity: the 7th triennial conference of the World Association of Theoritical and Computational Chemists (WATOC 2005)|volume=771|issue=1|pages=19–26|doi=10.1016/j.theochem.2006.03.035|issn=0166-1280|arxiv=physics/0508076}}</ref>

:2 Cl<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub> → 2 Cl<sub>2</sub> + 7 O<sub>2</sub> (Δ''H°'' = –132 kcal/mol)

Cl<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub> 的 Cl−O−Cl 键角为 118.6°。中间 Cl−O 键的键长为 1.709 Å ， Cl=O 则为 1.405 Å.<ref name=Holl/> 在这个化合物里，氯达到了最高的[[氧化态|氧化态]] +7, 尽管这是一个共价化合物。

==反应==
七氧化二氯在[[四氯化碳|四氯化碳]]里和一级/二级[[胺|胺]]反应，产生高氯酰胺:<ref>{{Cite journal| first1 = C. D.| first2 = K.| title = Reactions of dichlorine heptoxide with amines| last1 = Beard| journal = Journal of the American Chemical Society| volume = 96| issue = 10| pages = 3237–3239| year = 1974| doi = 10.1021/ja00817a034| last2 =  Baum}}</ref>

:2 {{chem|RNH|2}} + {{chem|Cl|2|O|7}} → 2 {{chem|RNHClO|3}} + {{chem|H|2|O}}
:2 {{chem|R|2|NH}} + {{chem|Cl|2|O|7}} → 2 {{chem|R|2|NClO|3}} + {{chem|H|2|O}}

它还与[[烯烃|烯烃]]反应，生成高氯酸烷基酯。举个例子，它会和[[丙烯|丙烯]]四氯化碳溶液反应，生成高氯酰异丙基和1-氯-2-丙基高氯酸酯。<ref>{{Cite journal| first1 = K. .| title = Reactions of dichlorine heptoxide with olefins| journal = The Journal of Organic Chemistry| last1 = Baum| volume = 41| issue = 9| pages = 1663–1665| year = 1976| doi = 10.1021/jo00871a048}}</ref>

七氧化二氯和[[醇|醇]]的反应会生成高氯酸酯。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=96|issue=10|language=en|issn=0002-7863|date=1974-05|pages=3233–3237|doi=10.1021/ja00817a033|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja00817a033|title=Reactions of dichlorine heptoxide with alcohols|accessdate=2022-02-02|author=Kurt Baum, Charles D. Beard|archive-date=2022-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220425201608/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja00817a033}}</ref>

七氧化二氯是一种强酸性氧化物，在溶液中与高氯酸形成平衡。

==安全性==

虽然它是氯的氧化物里最稳定的, Cl<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub> 仍然是一种强氧化剂，也是一种可通过火焰或机械冲击或与[[碘|碘]]接触而引爆的爆炸物。<ref>{{cite book
| title = Lewis' dictionary of toxicology
| first1 = Robert Alan
| last1 = Lewis
| publisher = CRC Press
| year = 1998
| isbn = 1-56670-223-2
| page = [https://archive.org/details/lewisdictionaryo0000lewi/page/260 260]
| url-access = registration
| url = https://archive.org/details/lewisdictionaryo0000lewi/page/260
}}</ref> 但是，它的氧化性不如其他氯的氧化物强，并且在低温时不会侵蚀[[硫|硫]]，[[磷|磷]]或[[纸|纸]]。<ref name="Holl" /> 它对人体具有与元素[[氯|氯]]相同的作用，并且需要相同的预防措施。<ref>{{cite encyclopedia
